result.name: Chiu Chow Delicacies

reviews.text: Food not bad but kinda expensive considering the environment and service
Great Teochew cuisine.. Nothing fanciful about its service or decor..
delicious. One of my fav restaurant in HK

April, 2017

Found this restaurant on Openrice.  Amazing authentic chiu chow food!  Will return for more.  You have to try the oyster congee and the Chiu Chow style beef noodle!!! Too bad they don't serve oyster pancake at lunch time =(

Update:  April, 2018

Finally get to visit this restaurant again and this time for dinnner!  My fav dish deep fried oyster pancake is available!!! This restaurant held up it's quality of food since my last visit!

Update Jan, 2019

Another trip to HK and can't get enough of this place.  Still taste good as expected.  The quality of food has held up well! =)
Good Food, but still need to wait even you have reservations, business too good.

result.name: 串燒食堂

reviews.text: 食物選擇多，質數好。一班朋友試了二十多款，差不多樣樣都好好味，價錢合理。老闆友善，服務一流。值得支持的家庭式小店。
The quality of the food is very good and the price is reasonable.
除左時間耐咗少少之外 無咩缺點😃
家庭式深宵食堂，價錢還算合理。

食過一次，念念不忘，不到兩星期又再去多一次。很有誠意的串燒店，每樣食物的味道都很好，沒有一樣令人失望。價錢不貴，款式又多，除串燒外，也有沙律，菜蔬，飯，烏冬。。等。試了不同的食物，各樣都做得很好，值得推介👍
其中有最特別的可算是燒羊皮串，另外有鹽燒法國鵝肝，蒜蓉燒蠔，厚切牛舌芯，汁燒鷄肝，車打芝士翠肉瓜，燒菠蘿，鹽燒秋葵，汁燒豆腐。。。樣樣都好正！😋😋😋
